   <meta name="author" content="Yarlet Partners"><meta name="description" content="Yarlet Partners: Angel Investment, Mentoring, Interim Sales Management, Start-up and early stage company advice within Software and Technology"><meta name="keywords" content="sales and marketing support interim sales management director angel investment early stage sales support"><title>Home - Yarlet Partners</title><link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" media="all" href="main.css"><link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" media="all" href="colorschemes/colorscheme2/colorscheme.css"><link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" media="all" href="style.css"><link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" media="all" href="style1.css"><script type="text/javascript" src="live_tinc.js"></script></head><body id="main_body"><div id="container"><div id="header"><div id="main_nav_container"><ul id="main_nav_list"><li><a class="navimain_current" href="index.html"><span class="hidden">Home</span></a></li></ul></div><div id="key_visual"><div id="logo"></div></div></div><div id="main_container"><div class="sub_nav_container"></div><div id="left_column_container"><div id="sub_container1"></div></div><div id="sub_container2"><div id="text_caption">Yarlet Partners:  Investment, Advice and Interim</div><div id="content_container" class="content"><div>Software and Digital Marketing companies are often founded by technologists. &nbsp;This is a good! &nbsp;Where the challenge starts is when growth begins or &nbsp;doesn't. &nbsp;Creating, implementing and managing a sales proposition without a background in business development or marketing trips up many an aspiring business. Its hard to plan, difficult to execute and harder to manage.</div><div><br></div>Yarlet Partners provides sales and marketing support to early stage and start-up companies within the software and technology space. &nbsp;This support is typically focused around : -<div><ul><li><span style="line-height:1.6;">Angel Investment - Individually or as a group upto Â£200,000</span></li><li><span style="line-height:1.6;">Advice - Mentoring, sales planning, getting your business investment ready</span></li><li><span style="line-height:1.6;">Interim - Hands-on leadership to kick start the sales proposition or expand to new territories and markets</span></li></ul></div><div><span style="line-height:1.6;">As founder of Yarlet Partners I have over 25 years in business development , all within software and services companies, big and small. &nbsp;Corporate end-user sales experience at Computacenter in the golden age of IT, &nbsp;the early nineties. &nbsp;Drowning in process and micro management at ICL leading upto the Millenium and then..</span></div><div><span style="line-height:1.6;"><br></span></div><div><span style="line-height:1.6;">In 2000 I co-founded smartFOCUS, a marketing analysis software company. &nbsp;In just four years we raised two rounds of Venture Capital finance and floated onto the London AIM stock exchange. &nbsp;This was driven by 12 straight quarters of increasing sales. &nbsp;Building sales propositions in End-User, Service Provider and Technology Reseller communities. &nbsp;Crucially breaking into the lucrative USA and Canadian marketplace via a network of business partners. &nbsp;Throughout this journey&nbsp;</span><span style="line-height:19.200000762939453px;">&nbsp;managing teams of mixed abilities across many time zones.</span></div><div><span style="line-height:1.6;"><br></span></div><div><div><span style="line-height:19.200000762939453px;">Of course you have to do everything else well, you business or product needs to work and be compelling. Many are, but struggle to be heard.</span></div></div><div><span style="line-height:19.200000762939453px;"><br></span></div><div><span style="line-height:1.6;">If your business wants to learn more?&nbsp;</span></div><div><br></div><div><b>Contact Details:</b></div><div><span style="line-height:1.6;">Founder: Jonothon Butters&nbsp;</span></div><div>email: &nbsp